high_descs: Turn left to face the shelf.
Pick up the banana from the shelf.
Turn around and walk to the microwave.
Heat the banana in the microwave and take the banana out.
Head to the fridge on the left.
Put the banana in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated banana in the fridge.

high_descs: Walk ahead to the shelf to the right against the wall.
Pick up the banana from the shelf.
Turn around and go straight ahead towards the microwave.
Use the microwave on the banana and pick the banana up.
Go to the fridge to the left of the microwave.
Place the banana in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Microwave a banana and place it in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and walk, turn right and walk, again turn right and head to the shelf.
Pick up the banana from the top rack of the shelf.
Turn back and walk, then turn right and head to the microwave.
Put the banana into the microwave, heat it up, and pick it up back.
Turn around and go left and turn right, head to the fridge.
Put the banana in the middle rack of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a banana into the fridge.
